seo: Lanproxy,CVE-2021-3019,目录遍历漏洞,检测,插件
summary: 该插件用于检测Lanproxy是否存在CVE-2021-3019目录遍历漏洞，通过读取配置文件来获取内部网连接凭据。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether Lanproxy has the CVE-2021-3019 directory traversal vulnerability by reading the configuration file to obtain internal network connection credentials.
